              <h1 class="page-header">About Us

              </h1>
              <p id="missionstatement">LPX, Logical Procurement Excellence, is about ensuring our customers are procuring their goods at the lowest cost, bringing more profit dollars to their organization which in turn aids them in being successful. With no ties to any distributor or products, our one and only mission is to assist our customers in maximizing leverage and profit.
</p>
