              <h3>Ray Schiffer
                  <small id="tagline">Co-Founder, President, CEO</small>
              </h3>
              <p>Ray, while being a co-founder, oversees the entire organization. His career expands over 35 years in the food service industry, holding many positions from delivery driver to President and CEO. He has a clear understanding of the difficulty of running a restaurant on a daily basis, as well as the distributors goal to meet earnings. The one constant that remains the same in the industry is that independent restaurants are paying two and half times the margins that the large chain restaurants have to pay. It’s Ray’s vision to bring procurement excellence and leverage to not only help the independent restaurants grow, but survive in this economy.</p>
          </div>
