                  <small id="tagline">Senior Vice President and General Council</small>
              </h3>
              <p>Mark has practiced law in the state of New York for over 3 decades and has worked closely with independent restaurant owners on a variety of issues. While being an attorney, he is still passionate about the restaurant industry in which he aids in the handling of all compliancy and contracts for the organization.</p>
          </div>


